cmpFileDates

public static boolean cmpFileDates(java.io.File src,
                                   java.io.File dst)
Compares the dates of the given files. File dates are only accurate to the second; therefore file dates are divided by 1000 and truncated (converting milliseconds to seconds).

Parameters:
src - The source file.
dst - The destination file.
Returns:
boolean true if the first file is newer than the second one, false else. If the second file doesn't exist false is returned.
